div.p: Ring-3 detection: (frame->cs & 0x3) == 3 triggers extra user_esp/user_ss pop by iret

text.tspan: if clear: send master EOI only,
2. pic_remap(0x20,0x28) BEFORE sti (prevents double-fault on IRQ0)
4. keyboard_init() install IRQ1 handler, zero buffer
IDT before PIC: guards against IRQ with no handler
PIC remap before sti: IRQ0 must NOT hit vector 8 (double fault)
sti last: nothing fires until all structures ready
